burlap.oomdp.stochasticgames

Class SGStateGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • burlap.oomdp.stochasticgames.SGStateGenerator
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ConstantSGStateGenerator

    public abstract class SGStateGenerator
extends java.lang.Object
    An abstract class defining the interface and common mechanism for generating State objects specifically for stochastic games domains. Unlike the similar StateGenerator class, this class requires a list of agents that will be in the world and will create an ObjecInstance for each agent that belongs the OO-MDP object class specified by each agent's SGAgentType.
    Author:
    James MacGlashan
